::Prowl::

He flew back around. He was relieved to have FireStrike off him but now
a new problem had come up. He opened a commlink.
"This is Prowl. Most of the Decepticons are retreating, but are troubles
are not over. The Decepticon know as Firestrike has managed to break
into the City. Activate auto defences, and lest get this guy."
He flew into the same hole in the roof, and landed. He was limping. He
stalked around with his acid gun. When he saw Firestrike he opend fire
four times.
